than me in this world.

32
00:02:36,590 --> 00:02:37,750
I also used to wish

33
00:02:39,430 --> 00:02:41,240
I had been born a boy.

34
00:02:49,120 --> 00:02:49,710
But

35
00:02:50,360 --> 00:02:51,430
now I think

36
00:02:51,870 --> 00:02:53,120
being a girl is better.

37
00:02:53,470 --> 00:02:55,000
I could make money
when I was a teenager,

38
00:02:55,470 --> 00:02:56,430
and once I made money,

39
00:02:56,590 --> 00:02:57,560
I could buy tons of

40
00:02:57,630 --> 00:02:58,470
pretty clothes.

41
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:00,150
And with pretty clothes,

42
00:03:00,150 --> 00:03:01,520
I could make even more money.

43
00:03:02,960 --> 00:03:04,710
Qian, you're not engaged in...

44
