129
00:06:56,190 --> 00:06:57,510
Sorry, I didn't hear you.

130
00:07:02,360 --> 00:07:02,750
Okay.

131
00:07:29,920 --> 00:07:30,680
Who's that?

132
00:07:32,310 --> 00:07:33,070
No idea.

133
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:34,870
Why do you look

134
