136
00:07:38,720 --> 00:07:39,950
But I'm getting used to it.

137
00:07:41,800 --> 00:07:42,800
Your hand...

138
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:50,390
This...

139
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:52,120
