168
00:08:59,390 --> 00:09:00,270
My superiors didn't

169
00:09:00,390 --> 00:09:01,510
approve my resignation.

170
00:09:01,960 --> 00:09:03,320
So I'm still in my old position.

171
00:09:04,960 --> 00:09:05,550
Han Shuang is

172
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:07,390
under investigation
by an investigation team.

173
00:09:07,910 --> 00:09:08,630
Your tape

174
00:09:08,630 --> 00:09:10,240
