175
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:12,440
What about Xingke?

176
00:09:14,510 --> 00:09:15,030
He'll serve

177
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:16,550
three years.

178
00:09:17,360 --> 00:09:18,600
Since it's a criminal offense,

179
00:09:19,150 --> 00:09:20,240
