181
00:09:24,320 --> 00:09:25,360
I went to see him once.

182
00:09:26,910 --> 00:09:28,030
You visited him?

183
00:09:30,440 --> 00:09:31,510
I tried

184
00:09:33,510 --> 00:09:35,270
