Please don't blame Wang Jia.

202
00:10:44,630 --> 00:10:46,360
I found her and begged her

203
00:10:47,510 --> 00:10:48,550
to give me your address.

204
00:10:51,200 --> 00:10:51,870
Wanzhi,

205
00:10:52,750 --> 00:10:53,670
tell you what?

206
00:10:54,870 --> 00:10:56,510
Every day since you left home,

207
00:10:58,670 --> 00:11:00,550
I've been blaming myself.

208
00:11:02,480 --> 00:11:03,550
So come home with me.

209
00:11:04,910 --> 00:11:06,030
I'm doing fine now.

210
00:11:06,840 --> 00:11:07,670
Really.

211
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:09,150
This is the first time

212
00:11:09,150 --> 00:11:10,480
I've found a job on my own.

213
00:11:10,670 --> 00:11:11,870
I can't quit halfway.

214
00:11:12,630 --> 00:11:13,390
But you have to

215
00:11:13,390 --> 00:11:14,790
