267
00:13:05,440 --> 00:13:05,870
Let's go!

268
00:13:06,360 --> 00:13:06,870
Don't you dare!

269
00:13:07,240 --> 00:13:07,630
Come on!

270
00:13:07,630 --> 00:13:08,390
Stop!

271
00:13:09,390 --> 00:13:10,120
Fang, don't be scared!

272
00:13:10,750 --> 00:13:11,480
No matter what

273
00:13:11,550 --> 00:13:12,000
