280
00:13:18,150 --> 00:13:18,960
Wanzhi, don't worry.

281
00:13:19,150 --> 00:13:20,030
I've called the police!

282
00:13:20,030 --> 00:13:20,480
Yeah!

283
00:13:20,750 --> 00:13:21,840
You misunderstood us.

284
00:13:22,480 --> 00:13:23,120
He's my...

285
00:13:25,630 --> 00:13:26,320
father.

286
00:13:30,200 --> 00:13:30,670
What...

287
00:13:32,870 --> 00:13:34,150
I really didn't expect

288
00:13:35,750 --> 00:13:36,870
you'd made so many friends

289
00:13:36,870 --> 00:13:37,960
here already.

290
00:13:38,320 --> 00:13:39,030
No wonder you don't

291
00:13:39,030 --> 00:13:39,840
want to go back.

292
00:13:40,270 --> 00:13:41,960
Oh, sir!

293
00:13:42,270 --> 00:13:44,030
I'm sorry. We got it wrong!

294
00:13:44,480 --> 00:13:45,000
It's okay.

295
00:13:45,320 --> 00:13:46,270
Sorry for the scene.

296
00:13:47,390 --> 00:13:48,440
With friends like you

297
00:13:48,440 --> 00:13:49,360
around her,

298
00:13:50,720 --> 00:13:51,480
