00:26:17,830 --> 00:26:21,590
Kiss...

595
00:26:21,590 --> 00:26:22,270
Knock it off!

596
00:26:22,830 --> 00:26:23,480
This is a work site,

597
00:26:23,960 --> 00:26:24,960
not a wedding chamber!

598
00:26:25,440 --> 00:26:26,440
Break time's over!

599
00:26:26,720 --> 00:26:27,480
Back to work!

600
00:26:39,200 --> 00:26:39,750
Juan?

601
00:26:40,880 --> 00:26:41,480
Juan!

602
00:26:42,160 --> 00:26:42,750
Coming!

603
00:26:43,720 --> 00:26:44,920
Hurry!

604
00:26:45,750 --> 00:26:46,880
We're waiting!

605
00:26:47,110 --> 00:26:47,720
Come on!

606
00:26:47,880 --> 00:26:48,750
Tell us everything!

607
00:26:52,880 --> 00:26:53,510
Actually,

608
00:26:54,440 --> 00:26:56,000
our families are about the same.

609
00:26:56,510 --> 00:26:57,880
His mother has eye problems.

610
00:26:58,000 --> 00:26:58,720
It's really bad.

611
00:26:59,590 --> 00:27:00,880
She almost can't see.

612
00:27:01,270 --> 00:27:02,110
He was worried I'd leave

613
00:27:02,110 --> 00:27:02,880
him if I found out.

614
00:27:03,550 --> 00:27:05,400
A blind mother-in-law?

615
00:27:05,960 --> 00:27:07,480
You'll suffer then.

616
00:27:07,830 --> 00:27:09,030
But it depends

617
00:27:09,070 --> 00:27:09,880
on her health.

618
00:27:09,960 --> 00:27:10,880
It's okay if she's fragile.

619
00:27:11,200 --> 00:27:12,480
Hao Qianqian, have some decency,

620
00:27:12,480 --> 00:27:13,310
alright?

621
00:27:13,680 --> 00:27:14,350
You'll have to look

622
00:27:14,440 --> 00:27:15,110
after her for years.

623
00:27:15,240 --> 00:27:16,270
I hope she lives a long life.

624
00:27:16,400 --> 00:27:17,880
I don't mind taking care of her.

625
00:27:18,310 --> 00:27:20,270
I hope you won't regret it.

626
00:27:20,480 --> 00:27:21,750
I won't.

627
00:27:23,070 --> 00:27:24,000
Mr. Zhou said

628
00:27:26,510 --> 00:27:27,640
no matter how heavy

629
00:27:27,830 --> 00:27:29,270
our family burdens are,

630
00:27:30,510 --> 00:27:31,790
as long as we're together,

631
00:27:32,550 --> 00:27:34,160
we can overcome the obstacles.

632
00:27:35,720 --> 00:27:37,440
You're so cheesy!

633
00:27:37,590 --> 00:27:38,640
A few nice words,

634
00:27:38,640 --> 00:27:39,550
and you got carried away.

635
00:27:41,590 --> 00:27:42,240
Li Juan,

636
00:27:43,350 --> 00:27:44,680
I wish you happiness.

637
00:27:47,440 --> 00:27:49,350
I wish you

638
00:27:50,030 --> 00:27:51,160
a life without hardship.

639
00:27:52,510 --> 00:27:53,790
As long as I'm with him,

640
00:27:54,550 --> 00:27:55,510
I don't mind a life

641
00:27:55,960 --> 00:27:56,720
of hardship.

642
00:27:57,830 --> 00:27:58,270
Great.

643
00:28:10,640 --> 00:28:11,720
So Mr. Zhou

644
00:28:12,070 --> 00:28:13,510
and Li Juan are officially a couple?

645
00:28:14,510 --> 00:28:15,000
Yes.

646
00:28:18,880 --> 00:28:19,920
I'm 26 now.

647
00:28:20,960 --> 00:28:22,270
My big brother got married

648
00:28:22,590 --> 00:28:23,310
when he was 21.

649
00:28:27,750 --> 00:28:29,000
My dad made a smart choice.

650
00:28:29,880 --> 00:28:31,160
He was the head cook at

651
00:28:31,240 --> 00:28:32,200
a state-owned factory

652
00:28:32,590 --> 00:28:33,790
with decent pay.

653
00:28:34,270 --> 00:28:36,030
But when they wouldn't
let me take over his job,

654
00:28:36,240 --> 00:28:37,160
he quit

655
00:28:37,640 --> 00:28:39,000
and brought me to Shenzhen.

656
00:28:39,480 --> 00:28:40,440
I didn't let him down.

657
00:28:41,030 --> 00:28:42,640
I became a pasta chef at 17

658
00:28:42,960 --> 00:28:43,830
and got my pastry chef

659
00:28:43,830 --> 00:28:44,960
certificate at 18.

660
00:28:45,440 --> 00:28:46,480
When I was 20,

661
00:28:46,920 --> 00:28:47,680
my father and I started

662
00:28:47,680 --> 00:28:48,640
running the cafeteria.

663
00:28:50,640 --> 00:28:51,880
I've been earning money for 10 years

664
00:28:52,550 --> 00:28:53,590
and saved quite a bit.

665
00:28:57,350 --> 00:28:57,960
Fang,

666
00:28:59,240 --> 00:29:00,510
your dad

667
00:29:01,070 --> 00:29:02,200
seems in civil service.

668
00:29:03,310 --> 00:29:04,830
Why didn't he pay for
you to finish college?

669
00:29:06,550 --> 00:29:07,680
He's my foster father.

670
00:29:08,750 --> 00:29:09,310
That makes sense.

671
00:29:09,830 --> 00:29:11,030
He only wanted to raise you.

672
00:29:12,110 --> 00:29:13,200
So he let you come to Shenzhen

673
00:29:13,920 --> 00:29:15,200
to pay him back?

674
00:29:16,880 --> 00:29:17,640
Sort of.

675
00:29:18,510 --> 00:29:19,200
Did you pay him?

676
00:29:19,590 --> 00:29:20,350
I can help you out.

677
00:29:21,350 --> 00:29:21,960
No, no.

678
00:29:22,400 --> 00:29:22,920
Thank you.

679
00:29:27,270 --> 00:29:28,480
Actually,

680
00:29:28,880 --> 00:29:30,350
a girl's family situation
doesn't matter.

681
00:29:31,480 --> 00:29:32,400
She just has to be kind.

682
00:29:33,200 --> 00:29:34,790
My parents only care about

683
00:29:35,400 --> 00:29:36,720
whether she can settle down with me.

684
00:29:39,000 --> 00:29:40,030
So that's what you want

685
00:29:40,240 --> 00:29:41,310
in your future wife.

686
00:29:41,640 --> 00:29:42,310
I'll remember that.

687
00:29:42,720 --> 00:29:43,590
If I find someone good,

688
00:29:43,790 --> 00:29:44,550
I'll fix you two up.

689
00:30:25,110 --> 00:30:27,030
Same for everyone!

690
00:30:27,240 --> 00:30:28,510
Soy milk for today.

691
00:30:28,720 --> 00:30:30,270
And with a smile.

692
00:30:31,680 --> 00:30:32,480
Add sugar yourself.

693
00:31:13,110 --> 00:31:13,480
Which one?

694
00:31:14,030 --> 00:31:15,720
- Tomatoes with eggs.
- Okay.

695
00:31:24,000 --> 00:31:24,480
Have some tea.

696
00:31:24,920 --> 00:31:25,550
Thanks.

697
00:31:26,590 --> 00:31:27,030
Juan.

698
00:31:30,160 --> 00:31:31,480
You're even calling her that now!

699
00:31:31,960 --> 00:31:33,070
But I'm telling you.

700
00:31:33,480 --> 00:31:34,830
Although you're older than me,

701
00:31:35,000 --> 00:31:36,440
I'll consider you my younger brother.

702
00:31:37,110 --> 00:31:37,550
Sure.

703
00:31:38,550 --> 00:31:39,270
I'll go with Juan.

704
00:31:39,590 --> 00:31:40,240
Whatever you want.

705
00:31:41,400 --> 00:31:42,720
Thank you for treating us!

706
00:31:44,110 --> 00:31:45,070
I should thank you, Fang.

707
00:31:45,310 --> 00:31:46,000
I heard about the advice

708
00:31:46,000 --> 00:31:46,680
you gave Juan.

709
00:31:47,440 --> 00:31:48,440
I admire how educated you are,

710
00:31:48,880 --> 00:31:49,790
and I agree with you.

711
00:31:51,680 --> 00:31:53,240
We met here in Shenzhen.

712
00:31:53,750 --> 00:31:54,200
So...

713
00:31:54,750 --> 00:31:55,350
I want to propose:

714
00:31:58,070 --> 00:31:58,640
the first cup

715
00:31:59,440 --> 00:32:01,720
to this city of innovation
and hard work.

716
00:32:04,480 --> 00:32:05,200
Wait, wait!

717
00:32:06,110 --> 00:32:07,680
You're treating us,

718
00:32:08,070 --> 00:32:08,830
but not with drinks?

719
00:32:10,510 --> 00:32:11,350
Excuse me.

720
00:32:11,680 --> 00:32:12,400
Rules in the army.

721
00:32:13,440 --> 00:32:13,960
How about this?

722
00:32:14,200 --> 00:32:14,830
You drink wine,

723
00:32:15,270 --> 00:32:16,400
and I have tea instead.

724
00:32:16,680 --> 00:32:17,830
No, no need!

725
00:32:18,030 --> 00:32:18,750
Too much trouble.

726
00:32:18,960 --> 00:32:19,750
It's okay.

727
00:32:20,240 --> 00:32:20,680
Cheers!

728
00:32:21,440 --> 00:32:21,920
Cheers!

729
00:32:29,200 --> 00:32:31,000
You're really splurging today!

730
00:32:31,270 --> 00:32:32,830
I love seafood!

731
00:32:32,960 --> 00:32:33,510
Can I go

732
00:32:33,590 --> 00:32:34,640
all out and eat?

733
00:32:35,270 --> 00:32:36,000
Of course.

734
00:32:36,680 --> 00:32:38,160
You're Juan's best friends.

735
00:32:38,310 --> 00:32:39,270
It's my treat.

736
00:32:40,960 --> 00:32:41,790
I think we have

737
00:32:41,880 --> 00:32:43,030
three days off this month.

738
00:32:43,160 --> 00:32:44,400
All construction sites are closed.

739
00:32:44,880 --> 00:32:46,480
Aren't you coming to find Juan

740
00:32:46,680 --> 00:32:47,750
and treat us again?

741
00:32:48,720 --> 00:32:49,310
What?

742
00:32:49,680 --> 00:32:50,270
Unfortunately,

743
00:32:50,920 --> 00:32:51,750
I'll go back to the army

744
00:32:51,880 --> 00:32:52,350
for a report.

745
00:32:52,510 --> 00:32:53,510
I won't be in town these days.

746
00:32:55,440 --> 00:32:56,590
So you two just got together

747
00:32:56,590 --> 00:32:58,030
and already have to separate?

748
00:32:58,270 --> 00:32:58,640
Parting is

749
00:32:58,640 --> 00:33:00,350
only for a better reunion.

750
00:33:01,350 --> 00:33:01,960
Mr. Zhou,

751
00:33:02,310 --> 00:33:03,550
have a safe trip.

752
00:33:04,240 --> 00:33:05,350
It's rare to have time off.

753
00:33:05,750 --> 00:33:06,830
Hope you all

754
00:33:06,830 --> 00:33:07,790
have a meaningful holiday.

755
00:33:08,440 --> 00:33:09,070
Thanks.

756
00:33:17,960 --> 00:33:19,880
Look at them.

757
00:33:20,790 --> 00:33:22,550
It makes me want to find someone too.

758
00:33:22,880 --> 00:33:24,310
I'm so tired all day.

759
00:33:24,590 --> 00:33:25,510
If I have a man

760
00:33:25,640 --> 00:33:27,110
to hold me when I get back,

761
00:33:27,160 --> 00:33:28,550
I'll sleep so well.

762
00:33:28,720 --> 00:33:30,480
Stop talking dirty.

763
00:33:30,550 --> 00:33:31,590
Why?

764
00:33:31,750 --> 00:33:32,880
It's just talk.

765
00:33:32,880 --> 00:33:34,350
We're all adults.

766
00:33:35,350 --> 00:33:36,960
Tell you the truth.

767
00:33:37,590 --> 00:33:38,720
The age on my ID

768
00:33:38,750 --> 00:33:39,720
is fake.

769
00:33:40,480 --> 00:33:41,640
I'm 26 actually.

770
00:33:41,830 --> 00:33:43,110
Why can't I think about men?

771
00:33:43,680 --> 00:33:44,480
Just think secretly.

772
00:33:44,720 --> 00:33:45,960
Keep it to yourself.

773
00:33:46,200 --> 00:33:47,720
I must say it out loud!

774
00:33:47,960 --> 00:33:49,070
Li Juan's off having fun

775
00:33:49,200 --> 00:33:50,270
with Mr. Zhou now.

776
00:33:50,400 --> 00:33:51,350
If I don't say it,

777
00:33:51,750 --> 00:33:52,880
I'll feel uncomfortable.

778
00:33:59,510 --> 00:34:00,550
We're having time off,

779
00:34:00,550 --> 00:34:01,790
but I'm not used to it.

780
00:34:02,960 --> 00:34:04,110
What took you two so long?

781
00:34:04,510 --> 00:34:06,110
You... you...

782
00:34:07,000 --> 00:34:07,750
What?

783
00:34:09,510 --> 00:34:10,880
Aren't you supposed to be with Zhou?

784
00:34:10,960 --> 00:34:11,760
Why are you back?

785
00:34:12,280 --> 00:34:13,800
I thought you'd stay overnight.

786
00:34:15,230 --> 00:34:15,840
Wanzhi,

787
00:34:16,550 --> 00:34:17,800
how come you're as bad as her?

788
00:34:18,920 --> 00:34:19,670
Come on.

789
00:34:19,760 --> 00:34:21,360
You two are officially a couple.

790
00:34:21,590 --> 00:34:22,230
Isn't that...

791
00:34:22,880 --> 00:34:25,000
normal to do it?

792
00:34:26,920 --> 00:34:27,880
But Zhou said

793
00:34:29,030 --> 00:34:30,320
we must get married first.

794
00:34:32,440 --> 00:34:33,000
Is there really

795
00:34:33,030 --> 00:34:34,280
such a pure man in this world?

796
00:34:34,320 --> 00:34:35,630
I can't believe it.

797
00:34:36,110 --> 00:34:37,320
So I took his sheets

798
00:34:37,320 --> 00:34:38,440
and covers

799
00:34:38,670 --> 00:34:39,360
and washed them

800
00:34:39,510 --> 00:34:40,150
while he's away.

801
00:34:42,400 --> 00:34:43,550
Then I have to

802
00:34:43,550 --> 00:34:45,230
interrogate you.

803
00:34:46,440 --> 00:34:48,360
How far

804
00:34:48,880 --> 00:34:51,030
did you two go?

805
00:34:51,150 --> 00:34:52,280
Did you...

806
00:34:55,110 --> 00:34:56,230
Why are you curious about details?

807
00:34:56,400 --> 00:34:56,960
I have to

808
00:34:56,960 --> 00:34:58,030
know details about you two.

809
00:34:58,150 --> 00:34:59,230
He is a man, after all.

810
00:34:59,280 --> 00:35:00,360
How could he be like that?

811
00:35:02,920 --> 00:35:03,880
Is something wrong with him?

812
00:35:05,510 --> 00:35:06,630
Shut up!

813
00:35:06,840 --> 00:35:07,840
He's perfectly normal.

814
00:35:08,800 --> 00:35:09,800
Did you check him?

815
00:35:10,710 --> 00:35:11,550
Hao Qianqian!

816
00:35:11,550 --> 00:35:12,360
She checked it!

817
00:35:12,630 --> 00:35:14,320
You... Qian, what do you...

818
00:35:14,400 --> 00:35:14,840
Hey!

819
00:35:15,030 --> 00:35:16,360
- You...
- Why are you panicking?

820
00:35:16,480 --> 00:35:18,110
Hey, what does it concern you?

821
00:35:18,590 --> 00:35:19,710
She's not concerned.

822
00:35:19,800 --> 00:35:20,670
She's jealous.

823
00:35:20,670 --> 00:35:21,190
Who said that?

824
00:35:21,190 --> 00:35:21,760
Hey!

825
00:35:22,150 --> 00:35:22,880
Hao Qianqian!

826
00:35:23,000 --> 00:35:24,960
How can you say that?

827
00:35:25,710 --> 00:35:26,880
Come catch me! Come on!

828
00:35:27,070 --> 00:35:28,400
That's too much!

829
00:35:32,230 --> 00:35:34,150
The cafeteria is closed
for the three-day holiday.

830
00:35:34,710 --> 00:35:35,440
The higher-ups

831
00:35:35,480 --> 00:35:36,840
are pretty nice to us.

832
00:35:37,710 --> 00:35:39,000
What do you guys want to do these days?

833
00:35:39,030 --> 00:35:40,070
Any plans?

834
00:35:40,670 --> 00:35:42,480
I actually want to go to the library.

835
00:35:43,070 --> 00:35:43,510
What?

836
00:35:43,760 --> 00:35:45,000
But I know you won't like it.

837
00:35:45,550 --> 00:35:46,550
So I'll go with your plans.

838
00:35:46,880 --> 00:35:47,960
I've been here for two years

839
00:35:48,070 --> 00:35:49,510
and haven't visited anywhere.

840
00:35:49,920 --> 00:35:51,190
I heard Window of the World

841
00:35:51,230 --> 00:35:52,280
is really famous.

842
00:35:52,480 --> 00:35:53,480
I wonder what it's like.

843
00:35:53,710 --> 00:35:55,670
It's a park with all
the global landmarks.

844
00:35:55,840 --> 00:35:56,590
It's worth visiting.

845
00:35:57,150 --> 00:35:58,190
Is the ticket expensive?

846
00:35:58,440 --> 00:35:59,710
Even if it is, it's worth it.

847
00:36:00,760 --> 00:36:01,360
Yeah,

848
00:36:01,760 --> 00:36:02,800
it's cheaper than going abroad.

849
00:36:03,960 --> 00:36:04,880
I

850
00:36:05,030 --> 00:36:06,920
want to go to the East
Lake Amusement Park.

851
00:36:07,320 --> 00:36:08,550
I heard they have a roller coaster.

852
00:36:08,590 --> 00:36:09,630
It's thrilling.

853
00:36:10,150 --> 00:36:11,480
Or we can go swimming

854
00:36:11,510 --> 00:36:12,400
at the beach.

855
00:36:12,550 --> 00:36:13,480
There are many foreigners

856
00:36:13,510 --> 00:36:14,840
in Guangdong.

857
00:36:15,280 --> 00:36:16,030
Maybe

858
00:36:16,440 --> 00:36:17,320
I can find

859
00:36:17,360 --> 00:36:18,550
a foreign boyfriend.

860
00:36:18,710 --> 00:36:19,840
Oh, come on,

861
00:36:20,000 --> 00:36:21,840
there you go again.

862
00:36:22,510 --> 00:36:23,440
Wherever we go,

863
00:36:23,920 --> 00:36:25,230
on the first night of the holiday,

864
00:36:25,360 --> 00:36:26,190
the three of us

865
00:36:26,190 --> 00:36:26,960
must go out

866
00:36:26,960 --> 00:36:27,800
and have a good drink.

867
00:36:28,000 --> 00:36:28,710
Get totally drunk!

868
00:36:28,760 --> 00:36:29,480
Agreed!

869
00:36:29,630 --> 00:36:30,440
Agreed!

870
00:36:32,510 --> 00:36:33,150
Over here! Come on!

871
00:36:33,630 --> 00:36:34,070
Here!

872
00:36:35,710 --> 00:36:36,590
The lamb skewers are ready!

873
00:36:38,630 --> 00:36:39,880
That's a lot of food!

874
00:36:40,030 --> 00:36:41,110
Not really. It's all here!

875
00:36:43,030 --> 00:36:44,550
FYI, I'm paying today, okay?

876
00:36:44,760 --> 00:36:45,840
No way, I'm paying.

877
00:36:46,440 --> 00:36:47,440
Mr. Zhou treated us

878
00:36:47,510 --> 00:36:48,710
to a fancy meal the other day.

879
00:36:48,920 --> 00:36:49,710
This one's cheap.

880
00:36:50,030 --> 00:36:50,590
When he

881
00:36:50,630 --> 00:36:51,920
treated you two,

882
00:36:52,110 --> 00:36:53,000
he didn't order drinks.

883
00:36:53,150 --> 00:36:54,030
I'll make up for it today.

884
00:36:54,360 --> 00:36:55,550
That's okay.

885
00:36:55,550 --> 00:36:56,960
Save your money.

886
00:36:58,590 --> 00:37:00,110
What's with you today, Qian?

887
00:37:00,280 --> 00:37:01,000
You want to pay?

888
00:37:01,110 --> 00:37:02,440
If you do, I won't fight you.

889
00:37:02,630 --> 00:37:04,440
Pay what?

890
00:37:04,630 --> 00:37:05,710
There are so many men here.

891
00:37:05,920 --> 00:37:07,320
Why should three pretty girls

892
00:37:07,320 --> 00:37:08,230
like us pay?

893
00:37:08,550 --> 00:37:10,190
We can just eat and enjoy ourselves.

894
00:37:10,400 --> 00:37:11,550
I'll take care of this.

895
00:37:12,000 --> 00:37:12,400
Cheers!

896
00:37:14,400 --> 00:37:15,440
Cheers!

897
00:37:20,510 --> 00:37:23,230
♪Sorrow deep, hearts entwined♪

898
00:37:23,440 --> 00:37:25,630
♪Only love fills our hearts♪

899
00:37:26,320 --> 00:37:29,000
♪The sea of love turns wild♪

900
00:37:29,150 --> 00:37:31,440
♪My true heart meets cold wind♪

901
00:37:32,230 --> 00:37:34,960
♪Parting ways, sky apart♪

902
00:37:35,150 --> 00:37:37,760
♪Will fate ever let us meet?♪

903
00:37:38,030 --> 00:37:42,880
♪The wind howls, crying in the storm♪

904
00:37:43,030 --> 00:37:48,000
♪Drifting through the crowd,
life is but a dream♪

905
00:37:48,590 --> 00:37:51,070
♪Deep love lives on♪

906
00:37:51,320 --> 00:37:53,480
♪Though eternity♪

907
00:37:53,920 --> 00:37:56,590
♪When snow falls and storms near♪

908
00:37:56,800 --> 00:37:59,440
♪May the flowers bloom in grace♪

909
00:37:59,630 --> 00:38:05,150
♪Not afraid of the mist
and rain along the way♪

910
00:38:05,440 --> 00:38:07,000
Bravo!

911
00:38:07,000 --> 00:38:09,230
Cheers! Cheers!

912
00:38:12,510 --> 00:38:13,400
Alright, boss!

913
00:38:14,320 --> 00:38:15,030
Come on!

914
00:38:15,440 --> 00:38:15,880
Coming!

915
00:38:16,360 --> 00:38:17,190
Their bill

916
00:38:17,400 --> 00:38:18,070
is on me!

917
00:38:18,480 --> 00:38:20,030
Bring six more beers

918
00:38:20,280 --> 00:38:21,150
and two dishes!

919
00:38:21,440 --> 00:38:21,800
Alright!

920
00:38:21,840 --> 00:38:22,920
Thank you, sir!

921
00:38:23,920 --> 00:38:25,840
- Have a good night, guys!
- Cheers, beauty!

922
00:38:29,480 --> 00:38:31,150
You're so crazy.

923
00:38:31,710 --> 00:38:32,920
Let's go somewhere else.

924
00:38:32,960 --> 00:38:33,880
Why?

925
00:38:33,880 --> 00:38:34,880
The guy already paid.

926
00:38:35,000 --> 00:38:35,960
Just enjoy it.

927
00:38:37,710 --> 00:38:38,320
Here you go!

928
00:38:38,590 --> 00:38:39,710
Beers from the man over there.

929
00:38:40,360 --> 00:38:41,440
Thank you, sir!

930
00:38:41,840 --> 00:38:42,480
Ladies,

931
00:38:42,760 --> 00:38:43,400
want anything else?

932
00:38:43,710 --> 00:38:45,110
Get us your

933
00:38:45,110 --> 00:38:46,510
best seafood!

934
00:38:46,920 --> 00:38:47,800
Alright, coming right up!

935
00:38:49,070 --> 00:38:50,400
You're really something.

936
00:38:50,670 --> 00:38:51,190
So what?

937
00:38:51,280 --> 00:38:53,150
I earn my own money.

938
00:38:53,670 --> 00:38:54,320
Let's drink!

939
00:38:54,710 --> 00:38:55,360
Hey, beautiful!

940
00:38:55,880 --> 00:38:56,960
Can you come

941
00:38:57,030 --> 00:38:57,880
and sing for us?

942
00:38:58,070 --> 00:38:58,760
Yeah!

943
00:38:59,440 --> 00:39:01,000
Sorry, she's not a singer.

944
00:39:01,710 --> 00:39:02,920
Ten yuan

945
00:39:03,590 --> 00:39:04,480
for a song, okay?

946
00:39:04,630 --> 00:39:06,280
Sir, we told you, she's not a singer.

947
00:39:07,550 --> 00:39:09,230
We don't even have a stereo.

948
00:39:09,280 --> 00:39:10,070
I have to sing alone.

949
00:39:10,110 --> 00:39:11,630
It hurts my throat.

950
00:39:11,840 --> 00:39:12,510
Twenty yuan!

951
00:39:12,800 --> 00:39:13,880
Alright.

952
00:39:14,150 --> 00:39:14,840
Hao Qianqian!

953
00:39:15,070 --> 00:39:15,480
Coming!

954
00:39:15,480 --> 00:39:16,710
What are you doing?

955
00:39:18,840 --> 00:39:20,840
What song do you want to hear, sir?

956
00:39:21,150 --> 00:39:22,320
What about Gathering?

957
00:39:22,760 --> 00:39:23,230
Okay! Great!

958
00:39:23,230 --> 00:39:23,960
Alright, ignore her.

959
00:39:24,280 --> 00:39:24,800
Let's eat.

960
00:39:25,440 --> 00:39:30,150
♪No matter how it ends♪

961
00:39:30,150 --> 00:39:34,960
♪At least we were together once♪

962
00:39:36,550 --> 00:39:37,880
Let's sing together.

963
00:39:39,800 --> 00:39:40,800
I can't sing.

964
00:39:41,840 --> 00:39:43,150
How can she sing?

965
00:39:43,920 --> 00:39:45,150
I'm not her.

966
00:39:45,360 --> 00:39:46,760
She's not here to sing either.

967
00:39:47,110 --> 00:39:48,670
She's just having fun.

968
00:39:50,030 --> 00:39:52,000
She charged for it!

969
00:39:53,030 --> 00:39:54,960
You're picking who to sing for!

970
00:39:55,320 --> 00:39:57,760
You respect him but not me?

971
00:39:58,400 --> 00:40:00,030
Hey, you're drunk.

972
00:40:01,070 --> 00:40:02,880
You're the one who's drunk!

973
00:40:03,960 --> 00:40:05,280
You're singing today!

974
00:40:06,070 --> 00:40:07,320
Or I'll beat you!

975
00:40:07,800 --> 00:40:08,550
Don't come over!

976
00:40:11,960 --> 00:40:12,670
Hey, man,

977
00:40:12,960 --> 00:40:14,150
leave the girls alone!

978
00:40:15,440 --> 00:40:17,190
Who the hell are you?

979
00:40:17,710 --> 00:40:18,760
How could you do that?

980
00:40:19,030 --> 00:40:20,400
He hit Mr. Gao! Let's beat him!

981
00:40:21,190 --> 00:40:22,280
Guys...

982
00:40:22,760 --> 00:40:24,190
It's a misunderstanding...

983
00:40:24,480 --> 00:40:25,630
He didn't mean it!

984
00:40:26,360 --> 00:40:27,070
He's just drunk

985
00:40:27,230 --> 00:40:28,030
and he lost his balance.

986
00:40:29,590 --> 00:40:30,440
You're drunk, right?

987
00:40:31,110 --> 00:40:31,480
Excuse us!

988
00:40:31,550 --> 00:40:32,800
Stop talking! Just come.

989
00:40:32,960 --> 00:40:33,630
Please excuse me!

990
00:40:33,920 --> 00:40:34,510
My pal is drunk.

991
00:40:34,670 --> 00:40:35,590
Sorry about that!

992
00:40:35,800 --> 00:40:37,030
Alright, alright.

993
00:40:37,150 --> 00:40:37,800
Come on, let's go.

994
00:40:38,030 --> 00:40:39,150
Alright, that's enough.

995
00:40:39,880 --> 00:40:40,190
You...

996
00:40:40,320 --> 00:40:40,710
It's okay.

997
00:40:40,710 --> 00:40:41,400
Everything's fine.

998
00:40:41,480 --> 00:40:42,800
You can sit down now. Go on.

999
00:40:50,480 --> 00:40:51,190
Fang Wanzhi,

1000
00:40:51,590 --> 00:40:52,480
you're really something.

1001
00:40:55,110 --> 00:40:56,150
He was drunk,

1002
00:40:56,150 --> 00:40:57,630
and you were actually
going to fight him.

1003
00:41:00,000 --> 00:41:00,710
Now I see

1004
00:41:00,710 --> 00:41:02,070
why you didn't finish college.

1005
00:41:02,190 --> 00:41:03,000
Did you get expelled

1006
00:41:03,030 --> 00:41:03,880
for fighting?

1007
00:41:08,360 --> 00:41:09,550
Wanzhi,

1008
00:41:10,150 --> 00:41:11,360
you know him?

1009
00:41:11,920 --> 00:41:13,280
No wonder he came to help you out.

1010
00:41:13,480 --> 00:41:14,590
Come have a drink with us.

1011
00:41:14,710 --> 00:41:15,550
I don't know him.

1012
00:41:17,400 --> 00:41:18,320
Thank you.

1013
00:41:18,960 --> 00:41:19,360
No problem.

1014
00:41:19,440 --> 00:41:20,920
You have to thank him anyway.

1015
00:41:21,800 --> 00:41:23,400
She wasn't like this before.

1016
00:41:24,110 --> 00:41:25,070
She's just drunk and upset.

1017
00:41:25,280 --> 00:41:26,280
I apologize for her.

1018
00:41:26,440 --> 00:41:27,360
Don't worry about it.

1019
00:41:27,670 --> 00:41:28,360
You guys continue.

1020
00:41:29,070 --> 00:41:29,710
Thanks again!

1021
00:41:37,190 --> 00:41:38,510
He knew your name.

1022
00:41:38,550 --> 00:41:39,840
Why did you say you don't know him?

1023
00:41:41,030 --> 00:41:42,400
He's just an annoying man.

1024
00:41:43,590 --> 00:41:44,800
I can't believe we ran into him.

1025
00:41:45,230 --> 00:41:46,590
Shenzhen isn't that big.

1026
00:41:49,670 --> 00:41:50,960
Are you okay, Mr. Gao?

1027
00:41:51,000 --> 00:41:52,480
Yeah, let's continue.

1028
00:42:01,000 --> 00:42:02,400
So much money!

1029
00:42:02,670 --> 00:42:03,920
If they hadn't messed around,

1030
00:42:03,920 --> 00:42:05,280
I could have made even more.

1031
00:42:06,710 --> 00:42:08,230
You actually want to sing for money?

1032
00:42:08,280 --> 00:42:09,360
Sing by yourself if you want.

1033
00:42:10,030 --> 00:42:11,070
I didn't do anything else.

1034
00:42:11,070 --> 00:42:12,590
Why can't I sing for money?

1035
00:42:13,000 --> 00:42:13,760
Men...

1036
00:42:13,960 --> 00:42:15,440
When they get drunk, they cause trouble.

1037
00:42:15,710 --> 00:42:16,510
When they're sober,

1038
00:42:16,510 --> 00:42:17,150
they won't spend

1039
00:42:17,150 --> 00:42:18,590
as freely.

1040
00:42:19,510 --> 00:42:20,510
I didn't expect so many

1041
00:42:20,550 --> 00:42:21,630
people at the night eateries.

1042
00:42:21,960 --> 00:42:22,840
I don't think we should

1043
00:42:23,000 --> 00:42:24,030
waste these three days.

1044
00:42:24,280 --> 00:42:25,190
Let's just sing there.

1045
00:42:25,400 --> 00:42:26,320
See how much we can earn.

1046
00:42:26,590 --> 00:42:28,000
Don't be so annoying.

1047
00:42:28,550 --> 00:42:29,400
Don't you see Wanzhi

1048
00:42:29,440 --> 00:42:30,480
was terrified just now?

1049
00:42:31,070 --> 00:42:31,880
Actually, I think

1050
00:42:31,880 --> 00:42:32,960
she's got a point.

1051
00:42:33,760 --> 00:42:35,280
If I had handled it gracefully,

1052
00:42:35,590 --> 00:42:36,760
it might not have ended like that.

1053
00:42:37,440 --> 00:42:39,760
Fang Wanzhi, what are you saying?

1054
00:42:41,670 --> 00:42:42,480
I came to Shenzhen

1055
00:42:42,670 --> 00:42:43,400
to work and earn

1056
00:42:43,480 --> 00:42:44,670
money with my own hands

1057
00:42:45,110 --> 00:42:46,760
and prove I can live well

1058
00:42:46,960 --> 00:42:47,800
by myself.

1059
00:42:48,670 --> 00:42:50,360
Qian taught me a lesson today.

1060
00:42:51,280 --> 00:42:52,590
I really want to try it.
